aries, manufactures and sells ball and roller bearings for original equipment manufacturers in India and internationally. The company offers a range of friction solutions comprising drawn cup needle bearings, cylindrical roller bearings, polyamide and steel needle bearing cages, drawn cup cylindrical roller bearings, crank pins, full-complement needle bearings, special ball bearings, thrust bearings, formed strip cages for heavy gearboxes, tapered and spherical roller bearings, rocker-arm bearings, planetary shafts, and other special pins. Its products are used in the automotive sector and mobility applications. NRB Bearings Limited was incorporated in 1965 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}